WEBVTT

00:00:00.714 --> 00:00:03.532
Kuna swali tunafaa 
kujiuliza:

00:00:03.556 --> 00:00:05.325
Kipi hakikwenda sawa?

00:00:05.349 --> 00:00:07.207
Si tu kuhusiana na janga

00:00:07.231 --> 00:00:09.231
lakini na uraia wetu.

00:00:09.544 --> 00:00:14.226
Nini kilichotuletea huu mgawano
na chuki kisiasa ?

00:00:15.147 --> 00:00:16.601
Kwa miongo ya karibu,

00:00:16.625 --> 00:00:20.895
utengano baina ya washindi na 
walioshindwa umezidi,

00:00:20.919 --> 00:00:22.910
na kutia sumu siasa yetu,

00:00:22.934 --> 00:00:25.133
kututenganisha.

00:00:25.157 --> 00:00:29.042
Mgawanyiko huu unahusu udhalimu kwa kiasi fulani.

00:00:29.577 --> 00:00:34.224
Lakini pia mtazamo
kuhusu kushinda na kushindwa